Theme
1. CTRL + WIN + K
2. Type "Configure", opens up 2 notepads.
3. Edit the "Read-Only" file on the left with the following theme:

[theme/Winblows]
opacity_back = 97
satellite_show = always
satellite_pos = topcenter
satellite_size = large
control_margin = 3
textbox_padding = 1
listitem_padding = 1
layout = list_icon,list_selmark,list_actions
color_background = #052429
color_foreground = #FFEAEA
color_title = #FFEAEA
color_textbox_back = #052429
color_faded = #aeb9c4
color_status = #FFEAEA
color_accent = #FFEAEA
color_warn = #cf433e
color_listitem_back = #052429
color_listitem_title = #FFEAEA
color_listitem_desc = rgba(255, 234, 234, 0.39)
color_listitem_tips = #FFEAEA
color_listitem_selected_back = #052429
color_listitem_selected_title = #FFD9D9
color_listitem_selected_desc = rgba(255, 217, 217, 0.86)
color_listitem_selected_tips = #FFD9D9
font_large_size = 18
font_large_style = bold
font_snormal_size = 10
font_snormal_style = cleartype
font_normal_size = 12
font_normal_style = cleartype
font_small_size = 10
font_small_style = cleartype
font_face = OpenSans-Semibold,Arial,Segoe UI
compact_results = yes
listitem_title_font = snormal

4. Edit the use file on the right hand side with:

[gui]
theme = Winblows

5. Save

Fix Catalog
1. CTRL + WIN + K
2. Right click --> Configure Package --> Bookmarks
4. Past into file on right side:

[provider/Firefox]
enable = no